        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer915548078" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13957173629187774151">The last, and one of the best, of a very long series of mysteries which have given me endless hours of enjoyment over the past twenty years or so. A very fitting and satisfying finale to a groundbreaking, classic collection of tales centered on one of the most engaging and admirable protagonists in mystery fiction. Thanks to Cadfael and his creator (note the small &quot;c&quot;), medieval England as depicted here will continue to enthrall those with the wit to appreciate it during this current century and</span>
  <span id="freeText13957173629187774151" style="display:none">The last, and one of the best, of a very long series of mysteries which have given me endless hours of enjoyment over the past twenty years or so. A very fitting and satisfying finale to a groundbreaking, classic collection of tales centered on one of the most engaging and admirable protagonists in mystery fiction. Thanks to Cadfael and his creator (note the small "c"), medieval England as depicted here will continue to enthrall those with the wit to appreciate it during this current century and beyond. Cadfael is timeless. RIP Edith Pargeter. Job well done.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13957173629187774151" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

